
Menu:
- Press ESC to quit (a swell option).
- Press Space to play:
	- Move with WASD and use the mouse to pan.
	- Mouse wheel switches between 1st and 3rd person.
	- Attempt to score the ball in the opposite goal!
	- Press R to restart or ESC to go back to the menu.
- Press ; for debugger:
	- WASD and mouse move the camera.
	- Q/E shrink/grow the interactable collision shape.
	- R rotates it.
	- Space switches the collision shape.
	- Sphere collisions sometimes don't register! That's fun!
	- Press ESC to go back to the menu.
	
